      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>The light mixer editor is a convenient window to allow you to edit multiple lights in the same interface.</p><h2 id=\"LightMixerEditor-OpeningLightMixer\">Opening Light Mixer</h2><p>You can open the light mixer editor from the scene properties <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"27\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689094&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=26&amp;height=27\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637312/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689094&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637324\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"scene_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637312\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e75b0282-2017-41cc-a860-b67884de802f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689094&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=26&amp;height=27 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689094&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=26&amp;height=27 1x\"></span> and clicking on the Open Light Mixer Editor</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"64\" data-width=\"919\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637342\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_LightMixer.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637312\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b8defb0e-8bbb-421b-b13a-225620fb311d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=919&amp;height=64 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=47 1x\"></span><p>Or, you can open it from the Object Context Menu.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=459\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"770\" data-width=\"1146\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637345\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_LightMixer2.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637312\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fe1e4db3-9588-40a4-a909-07d63f884da3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1146&amp;height=770 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/RenderManForBlender_LightMixer2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689498&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=684&amp;height=459 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"LightMixerEditor-CreateaMixerGroup\">Create a Mixer Group</h2><p>To create a group, click the + button on the right. A default name will be given to the group.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=607&amp;height=169\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637312/lightmixer3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"169\" data-width=\"607\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637333\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightmixer3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637312\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1c894e1e-a3df-4080-8a73-e418fa992ca2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=607&amp;height=169 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=607&amp;height=169 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"LightMixerEditor-AddLighttoGroup\">Add Light to Group</h2><p>Once you've created your group, you can add lights from the scene using the drop-down list, or do a search using the funnel icon.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=618&amp;height=343\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637312/lightmixer4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"343\" data-width=\"618\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637336\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightmixer4.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637312\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b0fd8cb3-95d8-4d1d-9246-3d5a2d2834b1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=618&amp;height=343 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=618&amp;height=343 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"LightMixerEditor-UsingtheLightMixer\">Using the Light Mixer</h2><p>Once you've added the lights to a group, you should see something like this.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"684\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=610&amp;height=341\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637312/lightmixer5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"341\" data-width=\"610\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637339\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightmixer5.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637312\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b3b9c812-9e25-40dd-be0d-79657b91d8cf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=610&amp;height=341 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637312/lightmixer5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689325&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=610&amp;height=341 1x\"></span><p>As you can see, the UI presents some of the more common parameters that you would edit on a light. From left to right:</p><ul><li><p>The &quot;-&quot; button allows you to remove the selected light from the selected group</p></li><li><p>The name of the light that you added</p></li><li><p>Temp: this allows you to switch over specifying a color temperature for your light.</p></li><li><p>Intensity: the intensity of the light</p></li><li><p>Exposure: the exposure of the light</p></li><li><p>The light bulb icon allows you to solo the selected light. If you solo a light, all other lights in the scene will be off</p></li><li><p>The eyeball icon allows you to mute a light, meaning that the light will be turned off in the scene.<br/><br/><br/><br/></p></li></ul>"
    }
  },
